Ambuye Yesu Kristu anati, “Ndipo Ine ndizipatsa moyo wosatha; ndipo sizidzaonongeka ku nthawi yonse, ndipo palibe munthu adzazikwatula m'dzanja langa, Atate wanga, amene anandipatsa izo, ali wamkulu ndi onse; ndipo palibe wina angathe kuzikwatula m'dzanja la Atate” (Yohane 10:28-29).
